wikipedia_page.main: Admiral George Ourry Lempriere (1787-1864) was an officer in the British Royal Navy during the Napoleonic Wars that rose to the rank of Admiral.

response: ** Frances Dumaresq m. Admiral George O. Lempriere (1787–1864)
Audley Lempriere was the son of Admiral George O. Lempriere and Frances Dumaresq of Pelham Place. His Great-Grandfather was Admiral Thomas Dumaresq through his mother's side.
